-- Arcapita to Gain $435 Million as It Completes IPO of Property Portfolio
-- B y   S h a j i   M a t h e w
-- 2010-10-25T06:49:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/arcapita-to-gain-435-million-as-it-completes-ipo-of-property-portfolio.html
Arcapita Bank BSC, a Bahrain-based
investment bank, completed a $920 million initial public
offering of its real estate portfolio, according to a company
statement e-mailed today.  “The exit has been achieved as a result of a successful
listing of the portfolio on the Singapore Exchange,” it said.
“The $920 million IPO will generate exit proceeds in excess of
$435 million for Arcapita and its investors.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
